OL,3,CAre we witnessing the decline of the
OL,4,CMidlands' clubbing industry?
OL,6,FA DJ from has told ITV News Central
OL,7,Fhe's having to rethink his career in
OL,8,Fthe nighttime clubbing industry
OL,9,Fbecause it's becoming financially
OL,10,Funsustainable.
OL,12,FIt's after entertainment company Rekom
OL,13,FUK announced the closure of 13 clubs
OL,14,Facross the country - including Pryzm,
OL,15,FPryzm and Jumpin Jaks.
