OL,6,FJames would normally be performing in
OL,7,Ffront of a packed out crowd of
OL,8,Fclubbers. Instead, the Wolverhampton
OL,9,FDJ, who used to work at Nottingham
OL,10,FPryzm, is now looking for work.
OL,12,FJames said: "It's been a real hard
OL,13,Fweek or two, I'd say, to have that
OL,14,Fnews. There is no redundancy pay.
OL,15,FThere is no physical support for you
OL,16,Fto fall back on. So you save the
OL,17,Fsecond you lose a job, you're
OL,18,Fessentially back out on the streets
OL,19,Fand you're fighting for work
OL,20,Felsewhere."
