OL,6,FHe continued: "And as hard as it is
OL,7,Fyou know, it pains me to say I don't
OL,8,Ffeel like this industry can give me
OL,9,Fthe stability that I need. So, I do
OL,10,Fthink sometimes, especially now more
OL,11,Fthan ever, that I do have to start
OL,12,Fthinking about a Plan B."
