OL,6,F"This outcome follows an extremely
OL,7,Fdifficult period for the late-night
OL,8,Fsector, thanks to the combination of
OL,9,Fthe cost-of-living crisis hitting
OL,10,Fyounger generations and students
OL,11,Fparticularly hard, as well as the
OL,12,Frising National Living Wage alongside
OL,13,Fincreased business rates and costs of
OL,14,Foperating.
